## How to Use

1. When an error occurs during any stage, append an entry here.
2. Link to the corresponding fix in `fix.log` using the entry date + stage as a key.
3. After resolving, update `lessons_learned.md` with what was learned.

## Common Error Patterns

| Pattern | Stage | Resolution Link |
|---------|-------|-----------------|
| GitHub Actions build failure | CI/CD | See fix.log |
| Navigation config mismatch | UI | See fix.log |
| Markdown render 404 | 6_Semblance | See fix.log |
| Azure Key Vault access denied | Secrets | See fix.log |
